Package io.smint.clapi.consumer.integration.app.target.json

Class SyncTargetJson

java.lang.Object
io.smint.clapi.consumer.integration.app.target.json.SyncTargetJson
All Implemented Interfaces:
io.smint.clapi.consumer.integration.core.target.ISyncTarget
public class SyncTargetJson extends Object implements io.smint.clapi.consumer.integration.core.target.ISyncTarget
Interface to implement for each synchronization target.

Contains a memory-only list of stored/updates assets and meta data. All data is lost as soon as this class is subject to garbage collecting.
